-- HUMAN RESOURCE MACHINE PROGRAM --

    JUMP     c
a:

    OUTBOX

    INBOX
    SUB      0
    JUMPZ    a
    INBOX
    COPYTO   0
    INBOX
    SUB      0
    JUMPZ    b
